      <title>vue项目报错合集</title>
      <link href="/post/vue%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E6%8A%A5%E9%94%99%E5%90%88%E9%9B%86.html"/>
      <url>/post/vue%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E6%8A%A5%E9%94%99%E5%90%88%E9%9B%86.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h2><p>本博客文章用于记录学习vue时遇到的一些问题报错等等（问题解决参考网上文章，仅作收录）（随时更新ing）</p><h3 id="问题1"><a href="#问题1" class="headerlink" title="问题1"></a>问题1</h3><blockquote><p>问题描述</p></blockquote><p>vue项目终端输入npm run serve报错error:03000086:digital envelope routines::initialization error</p><p><img src="/post/vue%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E6%8A%A5%E9%94%99%E5%90%88%E9%9B%86.htm/1.png"></p><blockquote><p>原因</p></blockquote><p>node版本太高</p><blockquote><p>解决</p></blockquote><p>在项目根目录下，终端输入以下命令修改环境变量</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="variable">$env</span>:NODE_OPTIONS=<span class="string">&quot;--openssl-legacy-provider&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后再次执行npm run serve即可解决</p><hr><p>有问题欢迎在评论区提出！</p>]]></content>
      
      
